column1: # "glemr11" remix - contains almost everything from revision 11 of lib_materials/lib_ecology,
#       (31st Aug 2019, dev branch). Some material of little value has been omitted. Code for
#       modifying terrain (e.g. producing lakes) has also been omitted
# The original mods were not suitable for use in survival mode, and the same applies to this remix.
#       Instead, this remix should be used as the basis for your own remixes. The section containing
#       ore packages can also be removed, as it is again not very useful in survival mode
# See the STANDARDS file for more information about what belongs in each category, and what does not
# (from craftitems.csv - dirt, clay, sand lumps, brick items)
# (from decorations.csv; items missing from other .csv files)
